# Template & Frontend Standards

## Templates
- All pages extend `base.html`
- Use `{% block title %}` and `{% block content %}`
- Use `url_for()` for all links and static assets
- Flash messages are handled globally in `base.html`

## CSS Architecture
- BEM-inspired class naming (e.g., `.stat-card`, `.stat-icon`, `.stat-info`)
- Custom properties in `:root` for colors, shadows, radii
- Mobile-first responsive design with `@media` breakpoints
- Use `var(--primary)` style tokens, never hardcode colors

## Components
- `.btn .btn-primary` / `.btn-secondary` for buttons
- `.dash-card` with `.dash-card-header` + `.dash-card-body` for panels
- `.badge .badge-success` / `.badge-warning` for status labels
- `.empty-state` for empty data placeholders
